## ğŸ§© æ‰©å±•æ–°æ¨¡å‹

è¦æ”¯æŒæ–°çš„ LLMï¼Œåªéœ€ç»§æ‰¿ `Caller` åŸºç±»ï¼Œå®ç° `call` æ–¹æ³•ï¼š

```python
from llmhive.caller import Caller, PromptContext
from collections.abc import Iterator

class MyLLMCaller(Caller):
    def __init__(self, model: str):
        self.model = model

    def call(self, ctx: PromptContext) -> Iterator[str]:
        # è¿™é‡Œå®ç°ä½ çš„æ¨¡å‹è°ƒç”¨é€»è¾‘
        yield "Hello from MyLLM!"
```

ç„¶åå°±å¯ä»¥åƒå†…ç½®çš„ Caller ä¸€æ ·ä½¿ç”¨å®ƒã€‚

